OL,7,FThe law campaigners want to introduce
OL,8,Fa legal duty of candour on public
OL,9,Fauthorities and officials to tell the
OL,10,Ftruth and proactively co-operate with
OL,11,Fofficial investigations and inquiries
OL,12,F` with the potential for criminal
OL,13,Fsanctions for officials or
OL,14,Forganisations which mislead or
OL,15,Fobstruct investigations.
