OL,4,C'must be all or nothing', campaigners
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FIn an update, Commons leader Lucy
OL,8,FPowell said the Government will take
OL,9,F"whatever time is necessary" to
OL,10,Fdevelop a law which "meets the
OL,11,Fexpectations" of the Hillsborough
OL,12,Ffamilies.
OL,14,FInquest director Deborah Coles said a
OL,15,Fdelay in a Bill being introduced to
OL,16,FParliament by the anniversary would be
OL,17,F"disappointing" but that it is
OL,18,Fimportant the proposed legislation
OL,19,Ffully meets campaigners' hopes.
