OL,4,C'must be all or nothing', campaigners
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,F97 football fans died as a result of a
OL,8,Fcrush at the FA Cup semi-final between
OL,9,FLiverpool and Nottingham Forest at
OL,10,FHillsborough Stadium in Sheffield. In
OL,11,F2016 an inquest jury ruled that they
OL,12,Fwere unlawfully killed amid a number
OL,13,Fof police errors.
OL,15,FSurvivors and the families of those
OL,16,Fwho died have been involved in a
OL,17,Flengthy campaign in pursuit of justice.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/19
