OL,3,CHillsborough Law to prevent cover-ups
OL,4,C'must be all or nothing', campaigners
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FMargaret Aspinall CBE, whose 18-year-
OL,8,Fold son James died in the disaster,
OL,9,Fsaid: "After hearing the stories of
OL,10,Fall the other families fighting for
OL,11,Fjustice, I am more determined than
OL,12,Fever to demand that the Hillsborough
OL,13,FLaw presented to Parliament is all or
OL,14,Fnothing.
OL,16,F"This is the legacy of families and
OL,17,Fsurvivors ` the bill has got to be
OL,18,Fright."
