OL,3,CHillsborough Law to prevent cover-ups
OL,4,C'must be all or nothing', campaigners
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FGrenfell United's Natasha Elcock said
OL,8,F"so many institutions and companies"
OL,9,Fhad tried to protect their reputations
OL,10,Ffollowing the 2017 west London tower
OL,11,Fblock fire which claimed the lives of
OL,12,F72 people.
OL,14,FShe added: "Why is it so easy for
OL,15,Fpublic and private agencies to escape
OL,16,Faccountability and scrutiny?
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@dO]vD@LOU
