OL,3,CHillsborough Law to prevent cover-ups
OL,4,C'must be all or nothing', campaigners
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,F"Establishing a duty of candour could
OL,8,Fprevent this, help us learn from
OL,9,Ffailures and ensure bereaved and
OL,10,Fsurvivors are properly supported. This
OL,11,Fis why a Hillsborough Law is so
OL,12,Furgent."
OL,14,FMayor of Greater Manchester Andy
OL,15,FBurnham put forward a Private Member's
OL,16,FBill called the Public Authorities
OL,17,F(Accountability) Bill in 2017 when he
OL,18,Fwas an MP, drafted by lawyers who had
OL,19,Facted for Hillsborough families.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@HO]
