OL,3,CHillsborough Law to prevent cover-ups
OL,4,C'must be all or nothing', campaigners
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FThe bill failed to be passed into law
OL,8,Fbefore Parliament was dissolved ahead
OL,9,Fof the 2017 General Election, but has
OL,10,Fsince been used as a starting point in
OL,11,Fthe new proposed Hillsborough Law.
OL,13,FHe said: "We are pleased the
OL,14,Fgovernment has listened to what the
OL,15,Ffamilies are saying and is working on
OL,16,Fthat law now.
OL,18,F"There is a concern that it wont be as
OL,19,Fstrong as it needs to be. And it does
OL,20,Fneed to be rock solid, watertight.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/19
