OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F392A1744127310
OL,3,CHillsborough Law to prevent cover-ups
OL,4,C'must be all or nothing', campaigners
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,F"We see the echoes of Hillsborough
OL,8,Freverberating through the decades. We
OL,9,Fsee that in the Infected Blood
OL,10,Fscandal, the Post Office scandal and
OL,11,FGrenfell.
OL,13,F"It's too easy to cover up in this
OL,14,Fcountry, and its too difficult for
OL,15,Ffamilies to fight for justice against
OL,16,Fthose cover ups."
OL,18,FMayor of Greater Manchester Andy
OL,19,FBurnham says families need parity of
OL,20,Flegal funding of inquests where the
OL,21,Fstate is involved.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/19
