OL,3,CHillsborough Law to prevent cover-ups
OL,4,C'must be all or nothing', campaigners
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FMr Burnham added there needed to be
OL,8,F"wholesale change to the way Britain
OL,9,Fis run" but it is worth taking the
OL,10,Ftime to get it right.
OL,12,FHe added: "We have appreciated the
OL,13,Fcommitment from the top of government
OL,14,Fto get this right and we will work
OL,15,Fwith them to make sure that happens.
OL,17,F"This is a big change, make no mistake
OL,18,Fabout that."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/19
