OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F392A1744127310
OL,3,CHillsborough Law to prevent cover-ups
OL,4,C'must be all or nothing', campaigners
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FWaldman said: "The duty of candour is
OL,8,Fso important. It shouldn't have to be
OL,9,Fthere.
OL,11,F"People who aren't affected and aren't
OL,12,Finvolved in these processes will think
OL,13,Fit seems common sense that people
OL,14,Fshouldn't be able to lie during these
OL,15,Fproceedings.
OL,17,F"But through all the stories and
OL,18,Faccounts we heard on that day, people
OL,19,Fdo sadly.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/19
