OL,3,CHillsborough Law to prevent cover-ups
OL,4,C'must be all or nothing', campaigners
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,F"That's why it's needed and not only
OL,8,Fis it needed, but it must be backed up
OL,9,Fwith enforcement and the threat of
OL,10,Fprison ultimately."
OL,12,FAmos Waldman from COVID-19 Bereaved
OL,13,FFamilies for Justice UK (CBFFJ) says
OL,14,Fthe duty of candour is necessary to
OL,15,Fprevent people from lying during
OL,16,Fproceedings.
