OL,3,CHillsborough Law to prevent cover-ups
OL,4,C'must be all or nothing', campaigners
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FLobby Akinnola, also from CBFFJ, whose
OL,8,Ffather died in the pandemic, said:
OL,9,F"Those bereaved by Covid have seen
OL,10,Ffirst-hand how easily the truth is
OL,11,Fdelayed, diluted or denied.
OL,13,F"Without full implementation of this
OL,14,Flaw, the cycle will repeat. And
OL,15,Ffamilies will keep paying the price."
